# Blueberry bpm mirror list.
#
# repos.conf takes one line per repo:   core <url1> [url2 url3 ...]
# Extra URLs are mirrors; `bpm update` and every package download try each in
# turn and fail over. Put the geographically nearest mirror first.
#
# The index is ed25519-signed and every package is sha256-verified, so a mirror
# is an untrusted file server — adding one never weakens trust.

https://repo.blueberrylinux.org         # origin (Vienna, AT)
# https://us.blueberrylinux.org         # (planned) North America
# https://fr.blueberrylinux.org         # (planned) Europe (FR)
